{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"1fedeb90d6","title":"关于攻击太原所需兵力的问题","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"6a351c622b","index":0,"year":1948,"month":12,"day":28,"articleId":"1fedeb90d6"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji25","name":"毛泽东全集第25卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji25.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji25":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"50ad889005","type":"paragraph","text":"关于攻击太原所需兵力的问题口","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji25","articleId":"1fedeb90d6"},{"id":"b99629d75e","type":"paragraph","text":"（1948年12月28日）周、陈、胡：（一）关于要你们准备以主力出石家庄堵击北平逃敌一事，业已电告。这只是一种可能情况的准备，不一定实行，但你们应有此项准备。（二）关于将来攻击太原的兵力问题，请你们按照教我力量对比，确实计算后电告：是否增加杨罗联三个纵队即已够用，除杨罗取以外是否还需加调兵力，及是否还需从林罗以处抽调一部跑兵（在平建攻克后）。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji25","articleId":"1fedeb90d6"},{"id":"655e86e3fb","type":"paragraph","text":"军委","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji25","articleId":"1fedeb90d6"},{"id":"ba76bf4dca","type":"paragraph","text":"俭子[1]这是毛泽东为中共中央军委起草的给华北军区第一兵团副司令员蒙[2]杨罗职，指杨得志、罗瑞舞、取恩，当时分别任华北军区第二兵团","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji25","articleId":"1fedeb90d6"}],"page":{"id":"4109585cf9","publicationId":"maoquanji25","articleId":"1fedeb90d6","start":466,"end":466}}}},"__N_SSG":true}